{"tid":2051991,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"7.28暴動案 拘捕警未向少女施警誡 控方不再依賴其招認口供","createTime":"2020-06-05T07:39:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T10:02:55.000Z","uid":240362,"like":210,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"21f7337958e67a5e44494f79f269fbc825dcc255","tid":2051991,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:39:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200605/AL6C5VE2TS3YCRIP6BV67VVELQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200605%2FAL6C5VE2TS3YCRIP6BV67VVELQ%2F&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EuzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=45b6e8b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200605%2FAL6C5VE2TS3YCRIP6BV67VVELQ%2F&h=013ef6b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200605/AL6C5VE2TS3YCRIP6BV67VVELQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n去年7.28上環警民衝突，湯氏夫婦與一名少女被控參與暴動罪。辯方反對將少女的招認口供呈堂，指警員曾向她威迫利誘。法官郭啟安今指，該警員從未向少女施行警誡，望控辯雙方就此議題作表述。控方休庭商議後，認為警員就招認部份證供夾雜個人意見，故不再依賴少女的招認口供。"},{"pid":"9b73180265308bd7fad36ca901e58de4793e803c","tid":2051991,"uid":106875,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:41:17.000Z","msg":"無左招認口供咁指控咪弱左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ff57c9788bfc9542c6fd81c5f2d4d08ccf7bc5","tid":2051991,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9b73180265308bd7fad36ca901e58de4793e803c","tid":2051991,"uid":106875,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:41:17.000Z","msg":"無左招認口供咁指控咪弱左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:43:02.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"e85c75c7e86c12c05cb2cfca369d2cf2b15abb5d","tid":2051991,"uid":216664,"like":76,"dislike":3,"score":73,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:43:36.000Z","msg":"近排咁多呢類case想幫香港洗白？咪玩啦，香港已經冇法治架啦"},{"pid":"8bf0b85b18fd0cc5ebb18c2468ce8f8e1ddcad6f","tid":2051991,"uid":21545